0.3.4
-----
* Support $EDITOR and $VISUAL as editor commands

0.3.3
-----
* Minor internal simplifications

0.3.2
-----
* Allow local HEAD to be ahead of remote HEAD
* Handle case if there's no previous release

0.3.1
-----
* First version on crates.io

0.3.0
-----
* Rename command 'cargo-release' -> 'rusty-release'
* Rename option '--no-publish' -> '--no-cargo-publish'
* Rename option '--no-push' -> '--no-git-push'
* Add configuration file '.rusty-release.toml' 
* Configurable commit message, tag name and editor by '.rusty-release.toml'

0.2.3
-----
* Better handling of early exiting clap and terminal colors

0.2.2
-----
* Minor internal cleanup

0.2.1
-----
* Add options '--no-publish' and '--no-push'

0.2.0
-----
* Show commits from HEAD till last release beside of changelog in editor
